        title: 'Will our people actually adopt the change?',
        description:
          ' Absolutely &dash; but it takes more than just communication. We build real ownership by embedding change agents, tailoring engagement, and helping leaders model the change from the top down.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How do we avoid dips in productivity and service delivery during the transition?',
        description:
          'Change doesn’t have to mean chaos. With a phased roadmap, smart risk management, and real-time adjustments, we help you keep &dash; and possibly even boost &dash; productivity and service levels throughout the transition.',
      },
      {
        title: 'We’ve tried this before and it didn’t stick. Why will this be different?',
        description:
          'That <i>“this too shall pass” </i>  &nbsp;feeling is real &dash; and we get it. We start by understanding your culture and readiness, anchor everything in measurable behavior change, and track real progress. Plus, we recommend staying engaged after launch to lock in the wins and prevent backsliding.',
      },
      {
        title: 'How do we communicate this without causing fear or confusion?',
        description:
          'Good communication isn’t just about talking &dash; it’s about connecting. We help leaders deliver clear, empathetic messages that balance transparency with vision, and we make sure there’s space for two-way conversations along the way.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Do we even have the internal capacity to do this right?',
        description:
